<rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">Walls, East (north part)</rs>: reused in a bastion, east of the north-east gate, north of <xref type="inscription" n="1547" href="120211">12.211</xref> (=MAMA 538).</rs><rs type="lastLocation">Findspot (1975)</rs>
</p>
</div>
